nd appellant was indebted to first appellant in the amount of R73 429 797.  But for the fact that first appellant agreed to subordinate its claims in favour of other creditors, second appellant would  have had insufficient funds to pay its debts and would 
be commercially insolvent.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 
