 would be released from their obligations under the loan agreement with first appellant which would also release second appellant in respect of its claims under the supply agreement.  The effect of the settlement agreement was that first appellant acquired
 control of second appellant.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 
